default is \fBrepo/etc/reports\-configuration.xml\fP.
.TP
.B \-h
Print usage information.
.TP
.BI \-s \ statsfile
Use an alternative path for the statistics file. The
default is \fBrepo/etc/statistics.xml\fP.
